      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO FORWARD KENNY (2) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing second (23.03) at Richmond in a Grade 5 over 401m. Rates highly and will give a great sight. HOTSHOT LILY (3) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at Richmond Straight in a handy 17.34 beating Tino Banner. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has definite claims. DESPICABLE PEDRO (4) caught the eye when clocking a swift 17.69 over 324m at Richmond Straight three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Must include on winning run three back. DESPICABLE SWIFT (1) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (17.77), beaten 1.5 lengths. Well placed and gets her chance.",
